description: I love the main station in Prague. I often go there because I had luck many times before. But today things were different. I just started to look around when a boy approached me. Yes. You got it right. He approached me. He asked me for some change for the ticket-machine. Of course I offered him more than just my change. I started my interview-strategy. But while I was totally focussed on my conversation someone grabbed my shoulder from behind. Some security guys insisted that I should switch off my cam. Well, you can see yourself what happened next. Anyway. At least the boy didn´t leave. He lost all of his money with gambling and was more than happy about my offers.
title: Czech Hunter 13
